EncounterParticipantIdentifierSearchParameter

Parameter participant.identifier:token

Searches for Encounters by a given Practitioner eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Encounter?participant.identifier={identifier}

ResourceEncounter
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesEncounter
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
